  },
  {
    tip: 'Mobile is non-negotiable',
    explanation: 'Most clients view your portfolio on phones. Galleries must work perfectly on mobile with swipe, zoom, and fast loading.'
  },
  {
    tip: 'Show your range strategically',
    explanation: 'Organize by category or style. Don\'t overwhelm visitors - curate your best work that represents your ideal clients.'
  },
  {
    tip: 'Make contact effortless',
    explanation: 'Clear contact options, inquiry form, response time承诺. Remove all friction from the booking process.'
